        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Solid chess game]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I&#x27;m proud of the fact that I played a really solid game. I kept waiting and waiting, and then my opponent moved a bishop protecting the queen and promptly blundered the queen. After taking his queen, he resigned!</p><p><img src="/img/chess/2022-03-31-solid-game/board.gif" alt="solid game"/></p>]]></content>
